title: ECU (Joondalup) League Team!
body: Anybody from ECU want to start a league team? If you are interested message me in game (IGN: "Kaoss") or email me at "isaac_somerton30@hotmail.com" rank and position doesn't matter this is just for fun, although if there are too many people tryouts will be held for the best players.

replies.body: Have you managed to find people for this?

I cant seem to find any league clubs at ECU which is a bit disappointing. 
Let me know if you find something or give me an add if your still up for either making a team or just playing
Maggie 
IGN: Moggie
